{"tid":667632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑岩善宏於5月8日病逝，享年55歲","createTime":"2018-05-17T02:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T12:32:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac5eec21608f54dd1b3ffe812a27432eca0ff0c","tid":667632,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:13:01.000Z","msg":"扼腕的消息，《鬼神童子ZENKI》漫畫家黑岩善宏的妻子今天（5月16日）在黑岩善宏的部落格及twitter公告，黑岩善宏於5月8日病逝，享年55歲。<br />\n<br />\n公告表示，黑岩善宏因為心肌梗塞病逝，與世長眠。也表示由於事發突然，才會到現在才對外公告，葬禮也僅有親人參與。她也感謝大家對黑岩善宏作品的支持，而他的官網、部落格及推特也將維持現狀，作為他曾活在世上的紀念與證明。<br />\n<br />\n黑岩善宏妻子在twitter公告黑岩善宏過世的消息。（圖：翻攝自黑岩善宏twitter）<br />\n《鬼神童子ZENKI》原作是谷菊秀，漫畫由黑岩善宏繪製，1992年於日本集英社發表短篇，後來發行單行本，共12冊，台灣則由長鴻代理，也改編成電視動畫，是許多動漫迷心中的經典。<br />\n<br />\n黑岩善宏曾當過桂正和（I&quot;s作者）的助手，也受《無敵鐵金剛》作者永井豪影響至深，但後來在漫畫圈浮沉，曾畫過成人漫畫等題材，代表作即為《鬼神童子ZENKI》。"},{"pid":"9838a8b20c5ad5a59c380b9fe18e6351d9650848","tid":667632,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20180516124534-54ebae3dbda649e42c6d45b517227233-mobile.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20180516124534-54ebae3dbda649e42c6d45b517227233-mobile.JPG&h=cfeafb85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《鬼神童子》漫畫家黑岩善宏5月8日因心肌梗塞病逝。（圖：翻攝自youtube）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20180516game_comic001/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2F20180516game_comic001%2F&d=K5WjfG8rMEJ21Oddyi0VqDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d108aa46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20180516game_comic001/</a>"},{"pid":"38511d9db662ef2821908837870df6433f7fbd05","tid":667632,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f506aceda89e0df82af9c5f4c0b23c8660246b","tid":667632,"uid":22